eu.fbk.dkm.springles.base

Class ForwardingTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • eu.fbk.dkm.springles.base.ForwardingTransaction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Transaction
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BufferingTransaction, ContextEnforcingTransaction, DebuggingTransaction, InferenceTransaction, SynchronizedTransaction, UnmodifiableTransaction

    public abstract class ForwardingTransaction
extends ForwardingObject
implements Transaction
    Implementation of Transaction that forwards by default all method calls to a delegate Transaction.

    This class is modeled after the 'forwarding' pattern of Guava (see ForwardingObject). Subclasses must implement method delegate() which is called by other methods and must provide the delegate Transaction instance.
